#: src\introduction.md:50
msgid ""
"The safe API currently covers: molecule I/O in any OpenBabel format; basic "
"properties (formula, mass, charge, counts); atom/bond access; SMARTS "
"substructure matching; fingerprints and Tanimoto similarity; numeric "
"descriptors (logP, TPSA, …); 2D depiction to SVG; 3D coordinate generation; "
"force-field single-point energy and constrained geometry optimization; "
"partial charges; InChI/InChIKey identifiers; least-squares structure "
"alignment; stereochemistry perception; SMARTS-based structural transforms; "
"conformer search; periodic-table element data; residues (biopolymer/PDB "
"substructure); and spectral descriptors. See the [Feature "
"Tour](./feature-tour.md) for details."
msgstr ""

